Hey guys,

Thespian club, in collaboration with Crea Shakthi is proud to announce the
commencement of its campus theatre initiative 2016. We will put up
"Silence! The court is in session" by Vijay Tendulkar, to be directed by
Upasana Bhattacharjee and Rohitha Naraharisetty.

Auditions for all the parts are open. If you think you can act do turn up.
If you think you can't definitely turn up.

The auditions have been scheduled on the 8th of August, SAC entrance at
7:00 PM. A copy of the script can be found at Gurunath, Folder 3 new
machine.

Here's hoping to see tons of enthusiasm from you guys

Cheers,
Sunaina Bose
Thespian Convener
(2016-2017)



